            {
               "text": "### Prerequisites\n\nIn this phase, we will reinforce our knowledge of multiplication with the 4 and 5 times tables. For better understanding, we suggest previously studying the previous phase in order to reinforce the knowledge of the times tables already learned (<htcite0>).",
               "source": [
                  {
                     "type": 1,
                     "uuid": "f3531db0-fc3f-4708-88bc-5cf5122c19b1",
                     "text": "History Tracers Team",
                     "page": "Multiplying with the Body (Level 1)",
                     "date_time": {
                        "type": "gregory",
                        "year": "2026",
